 236:Core/Src/system_stm32wlxx.c **** /**
 237:Core/Src/system_stm32wlxx.c ****   * @brief  Update SystemCoreClock variable according to Clock Register Values.
 238:Core/Src/system_stm32wlxx.c ****   *         The SystemCoreClock variable contains the core clock (HCLK), it can
 239:Core/Src/system_stm32wlxx.c ****   *         be used by the user application to setup the SysTick timer or configure
 240:Core/Src/system_stm32wlxx.c ****   *         other parameters.
 241:Core/Src/system_stm32wlxx.c ****   *
 242:Core/Src/system_stm32wlxx.c ****   * @note   Each time the core clock (HCLK) changes, this function must be called
 243:Core/Src/system_stm32wlxx.c ****   *         to update SystemCoreClock variable value. Otherwise, any configuration
ARM GAS  /tmp/ccqUmKfw.s 			page 6


 244:Core/Src/system_stm32wlxx.c ****   *         based on this variable will be incorrect.
 245:Core/Src/system_stm32wlxx.c ****   *
 246:Core/Src/system_stm32wlxx.c ****   * @note   - The system frequency computed by this function is not the real
 247:Core/Src/system_stm32wlxx.c ****   *           frequency in the chip. It is calculated based on the predefined
 248:Core/Src/system_stm32wlxx.c ****   *           constant and the selected clock source:
 249:Core/Src/system_stm32wlxx.c ****   *
 250:Core/Src/system_stm32wlxx.c ****   *           - If SYSCLK source is MSI, SystemCoreClock will contain the MSI_VALUE(*)
 251:Core/Src/system_stm32wlxx.c ****   *
 252:Core/Src/system_stm32wlxx.c ****   *           - If SYSCLK source is HSI, SystemCoreClock will contain the HSI_VALUE(**)
 253:Core/Src/system_stm32wlxx.c ****   *
 254:Core/Src/system_stm32wlxx.c ****   *           - If SYSCLK source is HSE, SystemCoreClock will contain the HSE_VALUE(***)
 255:Core/Src/system_stm32wlxx.c ****   *
 256:Core/Src/system_stm32wlxx.c ****   *           - If SYSCLK source is PLL, SystemCoreClock will contain the HSE_VALUE(***)
 257:Core/Src/system_stm32wlxx.c ****   *             or HSI_VALUE(*) or MSI_VALUE(*) multiplied/divided by the PLL factors.
 258:Core/Src/system_stm32wlxx.c ****   *
 259:Core/Src/system_stm32wlxx.c ****   *         (*) MSI_VALUE is a constant defined in stm32wlxx_hal.h file (default value
 260:Core/Src/system_stm32wlxx.c ****   *             4 MHz) but the real value may vary depending on the variations
 261:Core/Src/system_stm32wlxx.c ****   *             in voltage and temperature.
 262:Core/Src/system_stm32wlxx.c ****   *
 263:Core/Src/system_stm32wlxx.c ****   *         (**) HSI_VALUE is a constant defined in stm32wlxx_hal_conf.h file (default value
 264:Core/Src/system_stm32wlxx.c ****   *              16 MHz) but the real value may vary depending on the variations
 265:Core/Src/system_stm32wlxx.c ****   *              in voltage and temperature.
 266:Core/Src/system_stm32wlxx.c ****   *
 267:Core/Src/system_stm32wlxx.c ****   *         (***) HSE_VALUE is a constant defined in stm32wlxx_hal_conf.h file (default value
